<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٧٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2594">‌أَبُو دَاوُدَ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">‌شُعْبَةُ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَدَّثَنِي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/0">‌رَجُلٌ مِنْ آلِ سَهْلِ بْنِ حُنَيْفٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5834">‌مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ عَمَّارٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4621">‌عَمَّارٍ </a>،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> قَالَ النَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ: <span class="c2">«لَا يَدْخُلُ الْجَنَّةَ دَيُّوثٌ»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>